{"word":"G2733 - κατοικία - katoikía - kat-oy-kee'-ah - Habitation","slug":"G2733","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατοικία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katoikía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-oy-kee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Habitation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>κατοικία</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Katoikia</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>kat-oy-kee'-ah</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> dwelling, habitation </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to cause to dwell, to send or bring into an abode </p> <p class='li260'><b>3.</b> to give a dwelling to </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: a primitive root <p />- TDNT entry: None <p />- Part(s) of speech: Noun Feminine <p />- Strong's: <i>residence</i>(properly the condition; but by implication the abode itself): - habitation. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2026\">G2026</a>, <a href=\"#/G2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3615\">G3615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3616\">G3616</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3618\">G3618</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3623\">G3623</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925\">G4925</a>"}]}